        </item>
        <item>
            <title>Google Chrome 宣布推三大 AI 功能，美国用家可率先使用</title>
            <link>https://unwire.hk/2024/01/28/google-chrome-121/fun-tech/?utm_source=rss&#038;utm_medium=rss&#038;utm_campaign=google-chrome-121</link>
            <comments>https://unwire.hk/2024/01/28/google-chrome-121/fun-tech/#respond</comments>
            <dc:creator>
                <![CDATA[Pickle Rick]]>
            </dc:creator>
            <pubDate>Sun, 28 Jan 2024 08:00:03 +0000</pubDate>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[科技新闻]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[google]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[Google Chrome]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[Google Chrome 121]]>
            </category>
            <guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1217110</guid>
            <description>
                <![CDATA[<p style="font-weight: 400;">Google 宣布推出 Google Chrome 121 版本，预计会推出三大 AI 功能，有助用家书写文字、整理分页及撤换主题，以应对竞争对手 Microsoft Edge 的威胁。</p><p style="font-weight: 400;"><img fetchpriority="high" decoding="async" class="size-medium wp-image-1217116 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/helpmewrite-694x463.gif" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/helpmewrite-694x463.gif 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/helpmewrite-1280x853.gif 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲ Google Chrome 121 版本，预计会推出三大 AI 功能</p><p style="font-weight: 400;">Google Chrome 新增 Help Me Write 功能，用法类似 Gmail，如用家不清楚该如何在网上发表言论时写得得体，可以在打字栏单击右键，再按下 Help Me Write，AI 就会协助用家书写。Tab Organizer 故名思义就可帮助用家分类收纳分页。而自动转换 Chrome 主题则可以选择主题及以动画或相片的方式出现。</p><p style="font-weight: 400;">暂时 Google Chrome 121 版本只开放予美国用家，香港用家可暂时使用设定内的「Experimental AI」功能，正式版本仍要等待官方公布。</p><p style="font-weight: 400;">资料及图片来源：<a href="https://blog.google/products/chrome/google-chrome-generative-ai-features-january-2024/#help-me-write">Google</a></p><p style="font-weight: 400;"><br /><b>相关文章:</b><blockquote><li><a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/01/03/malware-abuses-google-oauth-endpoint-to-revive-cookies-hijack-accounts/tech-secure/?utm_source=inter&utm_medium=related&utm_campaign=rp" target="_blank">黑客新招式盗用 Google 帐户，官方一键解决问题教学</a></li>&nbsp;<li><a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/01/28/googles-latest-ai-video-generator/ai/?utm_source=inter&utm_medium=related&utm_campaign=rp" target="_blank">Google 推影片生成模型 Lumiere　画面动作连贯顺畅</a></li>&nbsp;<li><a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/01/28/samsung-google-reportedly-testing-wear-os-5/life-tech/watch-wireless-home/?utm_source=inter&utm_medium=related&utm_campaign=rp" target="_blank">Wear OS 5 传今年推出   Galaxy Watch 7 系列或率先预载</a></li>&nbsp;</blockquote><br /><p>The post <a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/01/28/google-chrome-121/fun-tech/">Google Chrome 宣布推三大 AI 功能，美国用家可率先使用</a> appeared first on <a href="https://unwire.hk">UNWIRE.HK</a>.</p>
]]>
            </description>
